Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:13.34,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:15.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:18.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:22.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:26.55,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:30.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:33.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:36.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:40.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:44.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:48.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:50.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:54.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:59.09,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:02.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:10.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:12.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.93,0:01:14.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:18.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:25.00,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,140.389)}Poison Butterfly of the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:25.00,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,720.389)}Amazon, Gireela
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.14,0:01:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a breakdown, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster! It's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Papa's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past month, three cars have\Nbeen found at the bottom of this cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But none of the vehicles'\Noccupants have been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would go to that trouble\Njust to throw out a junker...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've done something\Nwith the people inside
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,then sent the car off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is,\Nwhy'd they choose here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's deep in the mountains...\Nand no one would see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. How do you get\Na driver to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see a girl waving, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you're about to\Nbe in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They rigged something on the\Nroad to cause an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Shocker's behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be certain yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't look\Nlike car paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it's toxic?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take it home\Nand analyze it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,These are Japan's\Nmain reservoirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They flow with potable water\Nto quench humanity's thirst.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nif we poison this water,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we can purge large amounts\Nof humans all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen well, Gireela!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fill these capsules with the\Npoison scales from your wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and drop them into the\Nreservoirs from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Shocker's\NOperation: Poison Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If we wish to sow enough\Nchaos to conquer Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I will need to drop a large\Nnumber of capsules all in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Gireela!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're scales from\Na butterfly's wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And very unusual ones, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A non-native species?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The shining part there\Nis a deadly toxin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a close call, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have had\Na seizure and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a butterfly collector
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,who brought a rare poison\Nbutterfly from the Amazon recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I read about that in the\Nnewspaper, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find that\Nnewspaper and ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the prisoners\NI've collected so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the prisoners to work as slaves,\Nmaking poison capsules at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the child as a guinea pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A glass, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink this, as a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfect success.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not in this one, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't put it back with the\Nones we haven't sorted through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not in this one, either.\NAre you sure you saw that article?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it ran off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it was Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You used it for something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, why do you blame\Neverything on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew Goro had it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey.\N- Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The address is\Nclose to that dam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Something's bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should split up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You wait for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me if\NI'll be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:08:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I call this butterfly\Nfrom the Amazon "Gireela,"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but it doesn't have\Nan official name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's the\Nfirst one ever caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it have any\Nspecial properties?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NWhen pursued, it fights back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It stings its pursuer\Nwith poison needles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Those pierced by the needles\Nimmediately die from the venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They call it the "devil\Nbutterfly" there,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and even if they see it,\Nthey give it a wide berth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing it's so rare just\Nmakes me want to see it more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I please have a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just wait one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pretty lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,These are just like those\Nscales from before...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew Shocker would\Nbe behind this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do with the\Nperson who lived here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker gave my life to the\Npoison butterfly of the Amazon,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to create a cyborg Gireela!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Open this door and fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Set the bomb to go\Noff in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll blow away the\Nhouse, and him with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They set a time bomb, did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,With just five minutes to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki's been gone a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an S.O.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the poison butterfly\Nof the Amazon, Gireela!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... Taki is crying inside.\NGo find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, it's a time bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to explode soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to Plan B!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:50.76,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?\NTachibana Racing Club here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:57.02,Italics,,0,0,0,,Would this be\NMr. Tachibana Tobei?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:03.67,Italics,,0,0,0,,I heard you were looking for\Na butterfly from the Amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A butterfly from the Amazon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'm sorry,\Nbut could you tell me who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:14.84,Italics,,0,0,0,,Miwa Kujo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kujo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, my friends were\Non their way to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't arrived yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they certainly arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the demon\Nbutterfly Gireela...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And now,\NI'll show you my true face!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Capture that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be our hostage.\NTake him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not their way.\NKeep your guard up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Should we check it out?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Let's wait\Nhere a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the kind of room where the\Nlights go black and a monster jumps out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You've survived, but not for much\Nlonger, Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come finish our fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out here, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The capsules for Operation:\NPoison Water are complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and the countdown has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation: Poison Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is their underground\Nbase, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell for our trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! They're planning\Nto poison the dam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Operation: Poison Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want him to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll die if I have to!\NJust stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw Hongo into a cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Gireela.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to put the\Nplan into motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Round up all the prisoners!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we'll drop a\Ncapsule into Okutama Dam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll tie weights to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and drop them into\Nthe poisoned water!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Gireela!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a special way to finish\Nyou off when this is all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:09.53,Italics,,0,0,0,,If I could only destroy those\Npoison capsules from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:12.36,Italics,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going\Nto do with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I kill you, I'll let you watch\Nas I drop these capsules in the dam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hongo!\N- Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... watch,\Nas I throw these capsules into the dam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, leave these to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.94,0:22:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:39.20,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground\Nwith a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:46.62,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:50.41,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning\Nwith a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:54.07,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies\Nwith a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:57.72,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:21:01.32,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:27.77,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:34.35,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:39.05,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes\Nwith a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:42.78,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies\Nwith a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:46.11,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:50.08,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:09.94,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Swimming through the\Noceans with a Rider Swim,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:20.38,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great dive flitting\Nthrough the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.38,0:22:24.15,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up whirlpools\Nwith a Rider Screw!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:27.78,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Dragging enemies down\Nwith a Rider Lung!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:31.66,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:36.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.69,0:22:59.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker will spare no method in\Ntheir quest for world domination,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:03.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,from a stab in the back to\Na poison butterfly's flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.02,0:23:04.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ride on, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:07.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shatter Shocker's next plot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.88,Cont,,0,50,140,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:13.60,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.84,0:23:13.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:14.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is Tsuchigumo Man Dokumond.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:17.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell uses Dokumond,\Nwho appears from the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:19.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,drags people down,\Nand reduces them to skulls,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.24,0:23:23.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in an attempt to steal a liquid\Nexplosive that can melt any metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:25.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider tries\Nto stop it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.27,0:23:28.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for more Kamen\NRider in "Tsuchigumo Man Dokumond."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:30.99,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(407.167,150.389)}Tsuchigumo Man
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:30.99,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs185\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(577.167,690.389)}Dokumond
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:40.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.30,0:23:43.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:45.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:48.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:50.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:52.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.57,0:23:54.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:55.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.29,0:23:58.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:04.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.08,0:24:07.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:11.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.58,0:24:15.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison Butterfly of the\NAmazon, Gireela
Comment: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsuchigumo Man Dokumond